        Create an instance of the Cleaner class and set initial cleaning parameters.
        Parameters:
        sourceFolder - The base directory to scan for an Eclipse Installation.
        destinationFolder - The destination folder for moving duplicates to
        dryRun - when false than duplicates are moved to the destinationFolder when true than duplicates are just displayed, no action is taken!
        mode - The cleaning mode that indicates the method for resolving duplicated artifacts.
